AUTHORS

Kostya Zolotarov <kostya.zolotarov@gmail.com>

BACKGROUND

I need a tool that would automate creation and maintenance of source code
modules. Invoked from command line, such tool would produce a source code
module. Produced source code module would contain a fixed set of empty
boilerplate files. The boilerplate files would describe the source code module
and define its format and structure. Example boilerplate files could be -
README, INSTALL, CHANGELOG, VERSION, etc.

